CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FWes Streeting has likened tech
OL,8,Fcompanies to the tobacco industry, and
OL,9,Fmedical leaders have compared the
OL,10,Fdangers of social media to smoking, as
OL,11,Fpressure grows on ministers to impose
OL,12,Fa ban for under-16s ahead of the
OL,13,Fclosure of an online safety
OL,14,Fconsultation.
OL,16,FThe Government's Growing Up In The
OL,17,FOnline World consultation, which
OL,18,Ffloated measures such an Australia-
OL,19,Fstyle social media ban for under-16s,
OL,20,Fapp curfews and limits on addictive
OL,21,Ffeatures, closes at the end of Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FIn his first intervention on the issue
OL,8,Fsince he quit Government earlier this
OL,9,Fmonth, former health secretary Mr
OL,10,FStreeting said: "Social media should
OL,11,Fbe treated like tobacco ` it's
OL,12,Fextremely addictive, bad for our
OL,13,Fhealth, and Big Tech is borrowing the
OL,14,FBig Tobacco playbook to avoid
OL,15,Fregulation.
OL,17,F"We've got to give our children their
OL,18,Fchildhood back.
OL,20,F"A ban for under-16s must be the
OL,21,Fstart, not the end.
OL,26,@rD@QOUyD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,F"We have given the pen to tech moguls
OL,8,Fto write our future for us.
OL,10,F"It's time to take the pen back."
OL,12,FMeanwhile, a report by the Academy of
OL,13,FMedical Royal Colleges submitted to
OL,14,Fthe public consultation said social
OL,15,Fmedia and smartphone use "ranks
OL,16,Falongside smoking and wearing
OL,17,Fseatbelts in cars as a unifying force
OL,18,Ffor the medical profession".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUrD@aO]wD@ZOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FDoctors are seeing a "wave of
OL,8,Fradicalised children" from exposure to
OL,9,F"hateful, addictive and grossly
OL,10,Fdistressing content", the report said.
OL,12,FOf the 454 doctors surveyed by the
OL,13,Facademy of 22 member royal colleges,
OL,14,Fhalf said they treated at least one
OL,15,Fchild a week whose mental distress or
OL,16,Fphysical injury was linked to online
OL,17,Fcontent.
OL,26,@oD@VOUpD@UO]qD@AOUrD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FThe report included harrowing stories
OL,8,Fof deaths and injuries from
OL,9,F"replicating acts of extreme
OL,10,Fpornography" and interests in violence
OL,11,For radicalisation.
OL,13,FFamilies who have lost relatives to
OL,14,Fharm linked to online platforms are
OL,15,Fset to meet Sir Keir Starmer on
OL,16,FTuesday and urge him to honour the
OL,17,FGovernment's promise to impose social
OL,18,Fmedia restrictions on under-16s.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FThere have been widespread calls for
OL,8,Fthe UK to follow Australia's lead on a
OL,9,Fprohibition, although there have been
OL,10,Fquestions about how effective it has
OL,11,Fbeen.
OL,13,FMinisters announced in April they
OL,14,Fwould introduce "age or functionality
OL,15,Frestrictions" on social media for
OL,16,Funder-16s regardless of the
OL,17,Fconsultation outcome, with proposals
OL,18,Fto be unveiled by the summer and plans
OL,19,Fto legislate before the end of the
OL,20,Fyear.
OL,26,@vD@QOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FThe concession by the Government came
OL,8,Fafter pressure from the House of Lords
OL,9,Fover the issue, led by Tory former
OL,10,Feducation minister and academy chain
OL,11,Ffounder Lord Nash.
OL,13,FPeers voted four times to press the
OL,14,FCommons into accepting an outright
OL,15,Fban, ending their stand-off with MPs
OL,16,Fonly after ministers agreed to
OL,17,Frestrictions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FLord Nash said: "The Government gave a
OL,8,Fcommitment to Parliament that they
OL,9,Fwould introduce some form of age or
OL,10,Ffunctionality restriction on social
OL,11,Fmedia for children under 16.
OL,13,F"We now expect them to deliver on that
OL,14,Fcommitment fully and in the shortest
OL,15,Fpossible timeframe.
OL,17,F"Hundreds of thousands of people have
OL,18,Fmade their voices heard, asking the
OL,19,FGovernment to raise the age for access
OL,20,Fto harmful social media to 16....
OL,26,@oD@QOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,F"And today the Prime Minister will
OL,8,Fmeet the bereaved parents who have
OL,9,Fcampaigned tirelessly to prevent their
OL,10,Fexperiences happening to anyone else.
OL,12,F"Please, just get on with it."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUtD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FEllen Roome, who believes her son
OL,8,FJools Sweeney died aged 14 while
OL,9,Fattempting an online challenge, said:
OL,10,F"I, and other families who have lost
OL,11,Fchildren to social media, will tell
OL,12,Fthe Prime Minister directly: Social
OL,13,Fmedia is a product, and like any other
OL,14,Ffaulty product causing the deaths of
OL,15,Fchildren, it should be restricted
OL,16,Funtil the companies responsible have
OL,17,Ffixed it and proven it is safe.
OL,19,F"We cannot go on with further
OL,20,Fspeculation ` we need clarity."
OL,26,@rD@AOU{D@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FBut another coalition of children's
OL,8,Forganisations warned that focusing
OL,9,Fsolely on age limits risked failing to
OL,10,Faddress the structural drivers of
OL,11,Fonline harms.
OL,13,FThe Children's Coalition for Online
OL,14,FSafety, led by 5Rights Foundation and
OL,15,Fincluding groups such as the NSPCC and
OL,16,FGirlguiding, demanded a broader
OL,17,Foverhaul of technology companies'
OL,18,Fbusiness models and product design
OL,19,Fchoices that keep young users hooked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FIn a joint statement, 25 organisations
OL,8,Fcalled for a ban on targeted
OL,9,Fadvertising and manipulative design
OL,10,Ffeatures; a ban on personalised
OL,11,Fservices for under 13s and default
OL,12,Fsafety protections for under-16s with
OL,13,Fpenalties for firms that fall short;
OL,14,Fstronger regulation of AI systems
OL,15,Fincluding child-focused risk
OL,16,Fassessments; and the creation of an
OL,17,Findependent online safety commissioner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FLeanda Barrington-Leach, executive
OL,8,Fdirector at 5Rights Foundation, said:
OL,9,F"We will not fix this by tinkering
OL,10,Faround the edges ` by tweaking
OL,11,Ffeatures or relying on age limits
OL,12,Falone.
OL,14,F"The issue is not a single product or
OL,15,Fsetting; it is built into the system
OL,16,Fitself, into business models and
OL,17,Fdesign choices that prioritise
OL,18,Fengagement, data extraction and profit
OL,19,Fover children's wellbeing.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,F"If a product were unsafe for children
OL,8,Foffline, it would not be allowed onto
OL,9,Fthe market. We must insist on this
OL,10,Fsame logic online.
OL,12,F"The onus must be on these businesses
OL,13,Fto demonstrate that their services are
OL,14,Fsafe for children and not on parents
OL,15,For children to navigate or manage that
OL,16,Frisk themselves."
OL,18,FThe NSPCC charity said tech companies
OL,19,Fprioritising profit over keeping
OL,20,Fchildren safe "cannot be allowed to
OL,21,Fcontinue".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@QO]|D@OOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FRani Govender, associate head of
OL,8,Fpolicy for child, said politicians
OL,9,Fmust set out a path "requiring
OL,10,Fplatforms to build safety into every
OL,11,Fdevice, feature and AI tool from the
OL,12,Foutset, preventing children from
OL,13,Fencountering harmful or illegal
OL,14,Fcontent and ensuring they can only
OL,15,Faccess ageappropriate services
OL,16,Fthrough risk-based age ratings `
OL,17,Fsomething that children and adults are
OL,18,Ftelling us they strongly support.
OL,26,@qD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,F"It also means ending the addictive
OL,8,Fdesign tricks that keep young users
OL,9,Fscrolling, gaming and watching for
OL,10,Fhours on end."
OL,12,FA Government spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"Everyone ` especially children and
OL,14,Fyoung people ` should be able to have
OL,15,Fa positive, safe experience online.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@NO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,F"That's why we are consulting on a
OL,8,Fwide range of measures, from
OL,9,Frestricting social media access to
OL,10,Fpotential app curfews, to ensure we
OL,11,Fget the balance right and protect
OL,12,Fyoung people from harm.
OL,14,F"We are still seeking views from
OL,15,Fparents, young people and experts
OL,16,Fbefore taking our next steps. More
OL,17,Fthan 70,000 people have already
OL,18,Fengaged, and there is still time for
OL,19,Fothers to share their views before the
OL,20,Fconsultation closes at midnight.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779753774
OL,3,CStreeting likens social media to
OL,4,Ctobacco as pressure grows for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,F"We are also taking wider action to
OL,8,Ftackle online harm. Through the Online
OL,9,FSafety Act, platforms have to give
OL,10,Fusers more control over the content
OL,11,Fthey see and stronger protections from
OL,12,Fharmful material."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/18
